description:
There were too many dope moments from San Diego, we had to come back with a part 2. And you know what goes great with some Guerrilla Bars?… NEW MUSIC!! My EP “Soulilloquies” is officially live on Spotify, Apple Music, Tidal and all the other ones too. Hit the link in below and go run those streams up 🚀✨

SOULilloquies EP:
https://open.spotify.com/artist/3XOZM0DtztbmC1IE3amUnn?si=B93nIyDkR0qmsK-dhzaj3A
